| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4619 — Recovery Inhibition (akira)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 8aeabfac-c7c5-5d14-b2ae-d5ca10147fcf"
